        <aside role="complementary" class="sidebar">
          <div class="logo__top">Charli's Book Box</div>
          <hr class="separator" noshade>
          <article class="author__bio">
            <img class="author__photo" src="/static/images/charli.webp" height="200" width="200" alt="Photo of Charli">
          <p class="author__info">I'm Charli. I'm a BYU-I student, bookworm, metalhead, horror lover, and web developer. <a href="/about/">More...</a></p>
